We were gifted these from another team that switched from FRC to FTC. They were in a box with other sensors and switches. I think both are the same. The opposite side just says www.divsys.com.

We tried image searches but didn’t come up with the exact item. They are probably several years old (from pre-pandemic at least, maybe older).

Any help is appreciated.
Thanks!
